    "course_title": "CLIMATIC ENVIRONMENTS OF THE PAST",
    "description": "Climate change at timescales from the last several million years to the last 100 years, with emphasis on more recent timescales. Examines how climate variability arises from interplay between external forcings, feedbacks within the earth system, and (more recently) human activity.",
